})

Using watchActions
Add a saga to our module
To help make this more clear, we'll add a saga to the example counter module included in the starter-kit.
The example below is a little awkward because it's a contrived example. In a real application I would recommend using redux-actions to create action creators and reducers that handle those actions. For the sake of clarity, we're trying to leave the example from the starter-kit in place.
